('Personal Protective Equipment', 'Tactical Law Enforcement Protective Equipment', 'Ballistic Protection', '01LE-01-ARMR', 'Armor, Body', 'Personal body armor intended to protect the torso and extremities against small arms fire.  This type of personal protective equipment is recommended for personnel involved with tactical operations.', 1, 0, 6, 27, 40),
