('Cyber Security Enhancement Equipment', 'Network Level Security', '...', '05NP-00-IDPS', 'System, Intrusion Detection/Prevention', 'Intrusion Detection and/or Prevention System (IDS, IPS) deployed at either host or network level to detect and/or prevent unauthorized or aberrant behavior on the network. Software and hardware (appliance) solutions exist.  This replaces item 05NP-00-IDS and incorporates more recent prevention technology.', 1, 0, 2, 7, 284),
