('Personal Protective Equipment', 'Tactical Law Enforcement Protective Equipment', 'Other Items', '01LE-02-BDUS', 'Specialized Clothing, NFPA 1975 or NFPA 2112', 'Battle dress uniforms (BDUs), coveralls and jumpsuits that are worn during tactical operations and are constructed of fabrics that will not contribute to injuries in the event of exposure to heat, spark, or flash fire.  Certified as compliant with NFPA 1975 or NFPA 2112.', 1, 0, 2, 49, 756),
