('Personal Protective Equipment', 'PPE Accessories', 'Other Accessories', '01ZA-06-PRPD', 'Padding, Protective', 'General protective pads to provide protection for elbows, knees, neck, and shins while conducting operations, including rescue operations.', 1, 0, 15, 8, 830),
