('Information Technology', 'Media Devices', 'Cameras and Surveillance Equipment', '04MD-01-LAMP', 'Equipment, Light Amplification', 'Light amplification (night vision enhancement) equipment, including hand-held, helmet mounted, or equipment-mounted tactical systems.  Includes hardware/accessories necessary for helmet/equipment mounting.', 1, 0, 46, 13, 955),
