('Interoperable Communications Equipment', 'Commercial', 'Priority Services', '06CC-05-PRTY', 'Priority Services, Communications', 'Services to ensure priority communication over common carrier media, such as cellular phones or telephone land lines.  Includes Government Emergency Telecommunications Service (GETS), NCS Telecommunications Service Priority (TSP) Program, and NCS Wireless Priority Services (WPS).', 1, 0, 5, 14, 988),
