('Interoperable Communications Equipment', 'Private', 'Land-Mobile Radios & Bases', '06CP-01-VOTR', 'Receivers, Voter', 'A device that evaluates the comparative strength and signal/noise ratio from multiple receivers on the same frequency, selects the "best" signal and retransmits.', 1, 0, 65, 14, 994),
('Interoperable Communications Equipment', 'Private', 'Bridging/Patching/Gateway Equipment', '06CP-02-BRDG', 'Equipment, Bridging/Patching/Gateway', 'Includes a wide range of equipment and software utilized to connect disparate communications networks.  Systems range from cords that can patch two radios to interface boxes that can link dozens of radios, phones, computers, etc. in multiple sessions.', 1, 0, 4, 4, 995),
