('Interoperable Communications Equipment', 'Private', 'Other Land-Mobile Radio Equipment', '06CP-03-ICOM', 'Intercom', 'System for hands-free (wired or wireless) communication for limited numbers of personnel in close proximity, such as vehicle crew members.  Includes systems designed for underwater use.', 1, 0, 98, 15, 997),
('Interoperable Communications Equipment', 'Private', 'Other Land-Mobile Radio Equipment', '06CP-03-MWAV', 'Radio, Microwave Link', 'Microwave link for remote control of radio base stations or for links between infrastructure components and other communication assets.', 1, 0, 4, 15, 998),
('Interoperable Communications Equipment', 'Private', 'Other Land-Mobile Radio Equipment', '06CP-03-NRSC', 'Cable, Non Radiation-Shielded Transmission', 'Non radiation-shielded transmission cable between base/repeater and antenna.', 1, 0, 61, 15, 999),
('Interoperable Communications Equipment', 'Private', 'Other Land-Mobile Radio Equipment', '06CP-03-PRAC', 'Accessories, Portable Radio', 'Speaker/microphone extensions to portable radios.  Sometimes used within encapsulated/partially encapsulated suits, where restricted access to radio equipment impedes normal portable radio operations.', 1, 0, 8, 15, 1000),
