('Detection', 'Chemical Detection', 'Portable', '07CD-01-DPFI', 'Detector, Flame Ionization (FID), Point, VOC', 'Flame ionization detector (FID) for point detection of volatile organic compounds (VOC).DIQCode: [D]', 1, 0, 5, 15, 1017),
('Detection', 'Chemical Detection', 'Portable', '07CD-01-DPFP', 'Detector, Flame Photometry, Point, Chemical Agent', 'Flame photometry detector for point chemical agent detection. DIQCode: [D,I,Q]', 1, 0, 3, 15, 1018),
('Detection', 'Chemical Detection', 'Portable', '07CD-01-DPIR', 'Detector, Infrared Spectroscopy, Point, Chemical Agent', 'Point chemical agent detector utilizing infrared spectroscopy.  These detectors may also have explosive detection capability when equipped with appropriate spectra libraries.  See Item 07ED-01-IRED. DIQCode: [D,I,Q]', 1, 0, 41, 15, 1019),
('Detection', 'Chemical Detection', 'Portable', '07CD-01-DPMG', 'Detector, Multi-sensor Meter, Point, Chemical', 'Multi-sensor meter with minimum of O2 and LEL for point chemical detection. DIQCode: [D,I,Q]', 1, 0, 4, 15, 1020),
('Detection', 'Chemical Detection', 'Portable', '07CD-01-DPPI', 'Detector, Photo-Ionization (PID), Point, Volatile Organic Chemical (VOC)', 'Photo-ionization detector (PID) for point detection of volatile organic chemicals (VOC).DIQCode: [D]', 1, 0, 6, 15, 1021),
('Detection', 'Chemical Detection', 'Portable', '07CD-01-DPRS', 'Detector, Raman Spectroscopy, Point, Chemical Agent', 'Point chemical agent detector utilizing Raman spectroscopy.  These detectors may also have explosive detection capability when equipped with appropriate spectra libraries.  See Item 07ED-01-LASR. DIQCode: [D,I][Note:  Replaces 07CD-01-DPFR.]', 1, 0, 54, 15, 1022),
('Detection', 'Chemical Detection', 'Portable', '07CD-01-DPSI', 'Detector, Ion Mobility Spectrometry, Point, Chemical Agent', 'Ion mobility spectrometry (IMS) or Differential Ion Mobility Spectrometry (DMS) detector for point chemical agent detection. DIQCode: [D,I]', 1, 0, 8, 15, 1023),
('Detection', 'Chemical Detection', 'Portable', '07CD-01-DPSW', 'Detector, Surface Acoustic Wave (SAW), Point, Chemical Agent', 'Surface acoustic wave detector for point chemical agent detection.DIQCode: [D,I]', 1, 0, 4, 15, 1024),
('Detection', 'Chemical Detection', 'Portable', '07CD-01-FTIR', 'Detector, Fourier Transform Infrared, Point, Chemical Agent', 'Point chemical agent detector utilizing infrared spectroscopy with Fourier Transform capability.  These detectors may also have explosive detection capability when equipped with appropriate spectra libraries.  See Item 07ED-01-IRED.  [Note:  Replaces 07CD-01-DPFR.]DIQCode: [D,I]', 1, 0, 84, 15, 1025),
